      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "requirement:<<PIS-2085 IPC SW Specification V3.0.docx >> 3.2.1.9 Gages"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The basics for any analogue gage is as follows:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "Read data value from a signal or sensor",
        "Filter data value using lag filters",
        "Apply any pointer position calibrations",
        "Present value on analogue Gage."
      ]
    },
