    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "WOW trigger condition:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "当Calibration =  any mode to RUN时 ，一旦非RUN or PROPULSION状态 进入 RUN or PROPULSION 即满足；"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "当Calibration =  CRANK to RUN时 ，一旦CRANK 状态 进入 RUN or PROPULSION 即满足；"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_OCD_Gages_SRC/image-2024-8-28_14-35-7.png?api=v2",
