    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Filter Method"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "void interpolate16 ( uint16 u16Value, const uint16 * u16X_point, const uint16 * u16Y_point, uint8 u8Size, uint8 * u8LastIndex, uint16 * u16InterpolateOut )"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "插值法"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_OCD_Gages_SRC/image-2024-8-28_16-10-28.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_OCD_Gages_SRC/image-2024-8-28_16-10-28.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "uint16 FilterInterpolatedValue ( uint8 index, uint16 u16InterPolInData, uint8 filterReset )"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lag Filter"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* This public operation  First order lag filter - 16-bit I/O, 8-bit coefficient (0-255). * Y[n] = Y[n-1] + c*(X[n] - Y[n-1]), where *   Y[n] is the new filtered outdata (Ynf). *   Y[n-1] is the old outdata (Ynf) *   X[n] is current input (Xnf) *   c is the filter constant (cPos when increasing cNeg when decreasing)."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_OCD_Gages_SRC/image-2024-8-28_10-33-35.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_OCD_Gages_SRC/image-2024-8-28_10-33-35.png"
    }
